description: She is not known as one who covers up. On Sunday, Amber Rose shared several racy pictures on Instagram that featured the video model posing in several racy ways.
title: Amber Rose wears skimpy leopard swimsuit to show off her impressive curves
title_page: Amber Rose wears skimpy leopard swimsuit to show off her impressive curves | Daily Mail Online
text:
She is known for her killer curves.
And on Sunday, Amber Rose showed them off in a racy photo shoot that she shared on her Instagram account.
The 32-year-old beauty wore a leopard print swimsuit to play a game of pool.
Scroll down for video
In one shot, the ex-wife of Wiz Khalifa laid down, abs curved up, on a pool table.
Pool balls scattered about, Amber placed a cue stick in between her pose.
The video model wore a pair of black, platform heels, hoop earrings and sunglasses.
Another shot features an up-close view of Amber, tattoos on full display.
The waist training spokesmodel pasted her tongue against the cue stick.
Her right arm held the stick, while her left arm showcased her long nail manicure, hand placed on top of it.
In the final shot, cropped blonde sat up on the table, back arched to exaggerate her figure.
Face turned towards the camera, Amber placed the cue stick behind her, appearing to shoot pool from a backwards stance.
The risque photos were taken by photographer Brendan Forbes.
The New York-based photographer has worked with Amber before, including Karrueche Tran and singer Cassie.
